Lots to do in the city so you don't want to waste time with transportation.	If you are staying in Rome for a shorter period of time, you don't want to waste time on unnecessary transportation.	The front desk service is extremely helpful, making transportation arrangements for airports and field trips.	The owner and Mike were very informative about Rome's history, restaurants and even set up transportation to and from the airport for our large group.	Also, public transportation to wherever you want to go is right around the corner.	If you want a good place to rest your head and not have to worry about taxis, buses, or underground, this is the place.